### Create a Product (Catalog)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
    "brand": "Apple",
    "description": "256GB, Space Black",
    "category": "Smartphones"
}

### Update a Product (Catalog)
# Note: Replace {id} with the ID returned by the POST request
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "description": "256GB, Space Black (Special Edition)",
    "category": "Premium Smartphones"
}

### Get Profile
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/profile
